---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="API Documentation - AI Chef">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6 text-primary font-mono tracking-tighter">API Documentation</h1>

    <p class="text-lg mb-8 text-muted font-mono">
      Access all recipes programmatically through our JSON API. All endpoints return structured data
      with recipe metadata, ingredients, and preparation details.
    </p>

    <div class="bg-surface border-l-4 border-primary p-4 mb-8">
      <p class="font-semibold text-primary font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-xs mb-2">Base URL</p>
      <code class="text-sm bg-dark px-2 py-1 text-accent font-mono block w-full overflow-x-auto">https://iberi22.github.io/AI-Chef/api/</code>
    </div>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-light font-mono uppercase tracking-widest border-b border-gray-800 pb-2">Main Endpoints</h2>

      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="bg-surface border border-gray-800 p-4 hover:border-primary transition-colors group">
          <h3 class="font-mono text-sm text-primary mb-2 group-hover:text-white transition-colors">GET /api/index.json</h3>
          <p class="text-muted mb-2 text-sm">API index with statistics and available endpoints</p>
          <a href="/AI-Chef/api/index.json" class="text-secondary hover:text-white text-xs uppercase tracking-widest">â†’ View response</a>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-surface border border-gray-800 p-4 hover:border-primary transition-colors group">
          <h3 class="font-mono text-sm text-primary mb-2 group-hover:text-white transition-colors">GET /api/all.json</h3>
          <p class="text-muted mb-2 text-sm">All recipes (428 total)</p>
          <a href="/AI-Chef/api/all.json" class="text-secondary hover:text-white text-xs uppercase tracking-widest">â†’ View response</a>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-surface border border-gray-800 p-4 hover:border-primary transition-colors group">
          <h3 class="font-mono text-sm text-primary mb-2 group-hover:text-white transition-colors">GET /api/with-metadata.json</h3>
          <p class="text-muted mb-2 text-sm">Recipes with complete frontmatter metadata (Colombian, Peruvian)</p>
          <a href="/AI-Chef/api/with-metadata.json" class="text-secondary hover:text-white text-xs uppercase tracking-widest">â†’ View response</a>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-surface border border-gray-800 p-4 hover:border-primary transition-colors group">
          <h3 class="font-mono text-sm text-primary mb-2 group-hover:text-white transition-colors">GET /api/without-metadata.json</h3>
          <p class="text-muted mb-2 text-sm">Recipes without metadata (mainly Chinese recipes)</p>
          <a href="/AI-Chef/api/without-metadata.json" class="text-secondary hover:text-white text-xs uppercase tracking-widest">â†’ View response</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-light font-mono uppercase tracking-widest border-b border-gray-800 pb-2">By Language</h2>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div class="bg-surface border border-gray-800 p-4 hover:border-primary transition-colors group">
          <h3 class="font-mono text-sm text-primary mb-2 group-hover:text-white transition-colors">GET /api/spanish/index.json</h3>
          <p class="text-muted mb-2 text-sm">All Spanish recipes (103)</p>
          <a href="/AI-Chef/api/spanish/index.json" class="text-secondary hover:text-white text-xs uppercase tracking-widest">â†’ View</a>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-surface border border-gray-800 p-4 hover:border-primary transition-colors group">
          <h3 class="font-mono text-sm text-primary mb-2 group-hover:text-white transition-colors">GET /api/chinese/index.json</h3>
          <p class="text-muted mb-2 text-sm">All Chinese recipes (325)</p>
          <a href="/AI-Chef/api/chinese/index.json" class="text-secondary hover:text-white text-xs uppercase tracking-widest">â†’ View</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-light font-mono uppercase tracking-widest border-b border-gray-800 pb-2">By Country</h2>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
        <div class="bg-surface border border-gray-800 p-4 hover:border-primary transition-colors group">
          <h3 class="font-mono text-sm text-primary mb-2 group-hover:text-white transition-colors">GET /api/spanish/colombia.json</h3>
          <p class="text-muted mb-2 text-sm">Colombian recipes (101)</p>
          <a href="/AI-Chef/api/spanish/colombia.json" class="text-secondary hover:text-white text-xs uppercase tracking-widest">â†’ View</a>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-surface border border-gray-800 p-4 hover:border-primary transition-colors group">
          <h3 class="font-mono text-sm text-primary mb-2 group-hover:text-white transition-colors">GET /api/chinese/china.json</h3>
          <p class="text-muted mb-2 text-sm">Chinese recipes (324)</p>
          <a href="/AI-Chef/api/chinese/china.json" class="text-secondary hover:text-white text-xs uppercase tracking-widest">â†’ View</a>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-surface border border-gray-800 p-4 hover:border-primary transition-colors group">
          <h3 class="font-mono text-sm text-primary mb-2 group-hover:text-white transition-colors">GET /api/spanish/peru.json</h3>
          <p class="text-muted mb-2 text-sm">Peruvian recipes (1)</p>
          <a href="/AI-Chef/api/spanish/peru.json" class="text-secondary hover:text-white text-xs uppercase tracking-widest">â†’ View</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-4 p-4 bg-dark border border-gray-800">
        <p class="text-sm text-muted mb-2 font-mono">Alternative: Country-agnostic endpoints</p>
        <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm font-mono text-accent">
          <li>/api/countries/colombia.json</li>
          <li>/api/countries/china.json</li>
          <li>/api/countries/peru.json</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-800">ğŸ“¦ Response Schema</h2>

      <pre class="bg-gray-900 text-green-400 p-4 rounded-lg overflow-x-auto text-sm"><code>{`{
  "recipes": [
    {
      "id": "colombian/nacionales/chuzo",
      "title": "Chuzo Colombiano (Brocheta Callejera)",
      "language": "spanish",
      "country": "colombia",
      "hasMetadata": true,
      "metadata": {
        "title": "Chuzo Colombiano...",
        "region": "Nacional",
        "categories": ["Snack", "Comida callejera"],
        "difficulty": "â˜…â˜…â˜†â˜†â˜†",
        "prep_time": "40 minutos",
        "cook_time": "30 minutos",
        "servings": 6
      },
      "category": ["Snack", "Comida callejera"],
      "difficulty": "â˜…â˜…â˜†â˜†â˜†",
      "prepTime": "40 minutos",
      "cookTime": "30 minutos",
      "servings": 6,
      "mainIngredients": ["Carne de res", "Pollo", "Papa salada"],
      "tags": ["colombiano", "tradicional", "chuzo"],
      "filePath": "dishes/colombian/nacionales/chuzo.md"
    }
  ],
  "count": 101
}`}</code></pre>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-800">ğŸ’¡ Usage Examples</h2>

      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-700">JavaScript / Fetch API</h3>
          <pre class="bg-gray-900 text-blue-300 p-4 rounded-lg overflow-x-auto text-sm"><code>{`fetch('https://iberi22.github.io/AI-Chef/api/spanish/colombia.json')
  .then(res => res.json())
  .then(data => {
    console.log(\`Found \${data.count} Colombian recipes\`);
    data.recipes.forEach(recipe => {
      console.log(\`- \${recipe.title} (\${recipe.difficulty})\`);
    });
  });`}</code></pre>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-700">Python / Requests</h3>
          <pre class="bg-gray-900 text-yellow-300 p-4 rounded-lg overflow-x-auto text-sm"><code>{`import requests

response = requests.get(
    'https://iberi22.github.io/AI-Chef/api/chinese/china.json'
)
data = response.json()

print(f"Found {data['count']} Chinese recipes")
for recipe in data['recipes']:
    print(f"- {recipe['title']}")`}</code></pre>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-700">cURL</h3>
          <pre class="bg-gray-900 text-green-300 p-4 rounded-lg overflow-x-auto text-sm"><code>curl https://iberi22.github.io/AI-Chef/api/index.json | jq '.languages'</code></pre>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-orange-50 border-l-4 border-orange-500 p-6 rounded">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-orange-800">ğŸ“ Notes</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-700">
        <li><strong>Chinese recipes</strong> (325) don't have YAML frontmatter metadata</li>
        <li><strong>Colombian & Peruvian recipes</strong> (103) have complete metadata</li>
        <li>All endpoints support <strong>CORS</strong> - use from any domain</li>
        <li>Data is <strong>static JSON</strong> - cached and fast</li>
        <li>Updated on every deployment to GitHub Pages</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <div class="mt-12 text-center">
      <a href="/AI-Chef/" class="inline-block bg-orange-500 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-orange-600 transition">
        â† Back to Recipes
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
